Toss shrimp, oil and Lemon Pepper. Grill shrimp until just cooked through. Set aside. Combine onion, cucumber and tomato. Add bread, basil and shrimp to salad. Toss with dressing and serve immediately. Dressing: Whisk together 1/3 cup olive oil, 3 tablespoons red wine vinegar and 1/2 teaspoon Lawry's(R) Lemon Pepper.